  decompositionDecl(hasAnyBinding(bindingDecl(hasName("f").bind("fBinding"))))
matches the decomposition decl with 'f' bound to "fBinding".

Matches the Nth binding of a DecompositionDecl.

For example, in:
void foo()
{
    int arr[3];
    auto &amp;[f, s, t] = arr;

