Matches VariableArrayType nodes that have a specific size
expression.

Given
  void f(int b) {
    int a[b];
  }
variableArrayType(hasSizeExpr(ignoringImpCasts(declRefExpr(to(
  varDecl(hasName("b")))))))
  matches "int a[b]"
